polis|location2=[[Washington, D.C.|Washington]]|location3=[[New Carrollton station|New Carrollton Station]]|extra=rail}}\n|notes=Signed as exits 19A (east) and 19B (west); exits 7A\u2013B on US&nbsp;50; access to New Carrollton Station from southbound ramp to westbound US&nbsp;50; eastern terminus of [[Orange Line (Washington Metro)|Orange Line]]}}\n{{MDint|old\n|location=New Carrollton\n|mile=19.59\n|exit=20\n|road={{jct|state=MD|MD|450|name1=Annapolis Road|city1=Lanham|city2=Bladensburg}}\n|notes=Signed as exits 20A (east) and 20B (west)}}\n{{MDint|old\n|location=Greenbelt\n|lspan=3\n|mile=22.12\n|exit=22\n|road={{jct|state=MD|BWP|name1=[[Maryland Route 295|MD 295]]|city1=Baltimore|location2=[[Washington, D.C.|Washington]]}}\n|notes=Signed as exits 22A (north) and 22B (south); no commercial vehicles}}\n{{MDint|old\n|mile=23.04\n|exit=23\n|road={{jct|state=MD|MD|201|name1=Kenilworth Avenue|city1=Bladensburg|city2=Greenbelt}}\n|notes=Access to [[Maryland Route 193|MD 193]], [[Goddard Space Flight Center]], [[University of Maryland]], [[Maryland Stadium]], and [[Xfinity Center (College Park, Maryland)|Xfinity Center]] <br> Northbound access to [[Greenbelt station|Greenbelt Metro station]] must use this exit\n}}\n{{MDint|old\n|mile=24.25\n|exit=24\n|type=incomplete\n|road=[[File:WMATA Metro Logo small.svg|20px|link=Washington Metro]]{{jct|extra=rail}} [[Greenbelt station|Greenbelt Station]]\n|notes=Southbound exit and northbound entrance; no commercial vehicles <br> Northern terminus of [[Green Line (Washington Metro)|Green]] and [[Yellow Line (Washington Metro)|Yellow]] lines\n}}\n{{MDint|old\n|location=College Park\n|lspan=2\n|mile=25.19\n|exit=25\n|road={{jct|state=MD|US|1|name1=Baltimore Avenue|city1=Laurel|city2=College Park}}\n|notes=Signed as exits 25A (north) and 25B (south) southbound}}\n{{MDint|old\n|mile=26.11\n|exit=27<!--only signed clockwise/inner-->\n|type=concur\n|road={{jct|state=MD|I|95|dir1=north|city1=Baltimore}}\n|notes=North end of [[concurrency 